==English==
===Noun===
'''transportability'''
#([[communications]]) The [[quality]] of [[equipment]], [[device]]s, [[system]]s, and associated [[hardware]] that permits their being moved from one [[location]] to another to [[interconnect]] with locally available [[complementary]] equipment, devices, systems, associated hardware, or other complementary facilities. 

#([[military]]) The [[capability]] of [[materiel]] to be moved by [[towing]], [[self-propulsion]], or [[carrier]] via any means, such as [[railway]]s, [[highway]]s, [[waterway]]s, [[pipeline]]s, [[ocean]]s, and [[airway]]s.